    <item>
      <title>由于强势美元削弱需求，油价从数月高点回落</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-pulls-back-multi-month-highs-strong-dollar-dents-demand-2024-03-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三亚洲早盘，油价小幅走低，因美元走强抑制了投资者的兴趣，而在基准指数在过去两个交易日均升至数月高点后，交易员纷纷撤资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-pulls-back-multi-month-highs-strong-dollar-dents-demand-2024-03-20/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 01:22:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
