      <title>Chipotle 董事会批准 1 股 50 股的股票分割</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chipotles-board-approves-50-for-1-stock-split-2024-03-19/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Chipotle Mexican Grill 周二表示，其董事会已批准将其普通股以 50 比 1 的比例分割，这使得该墨西哥卷饼连锁店的股价在盘后交易中上涨约 7%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chipotles-board-approves-50-for-1-stock-split-2024-03-19/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 22:21:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
