      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/futures-tread-water-ahead-fed-meet-2024-03-19/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街三大股指周二收高，此前热门芯片制造商英伟达的股价摆脱了早盘的跌幅，投资者期待周三美联储政策会议的结论，以寻找利率政策的线索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/futures-tread-water-ahead-fed-meet-2024-03-19/</guid>
